    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯爆炸物制造商使用肥料公司钝化制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/russian-explosive-makers-use-fertilizer-firms-to-blunt-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博社的文件，俄罗斯计划收到对制造爆炸物至关重要的化学成分，这些化学成分是从肥料公司命令的，这些公司在很大程度上逃脱了国际制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/russian-explosive-makers-use-fertilizer-firms-to-blunt-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 11:29:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚领导人要求蒂格里（Tigray）提议新的头部缓解紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ethiopia-leader-asks-tigray-to-propose-new-head-to-ease-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚总理阿比伊·艾哈迈德（Abiy Ahmed）邀请居民蒂格莱省的居民提名新的领导人，以缓解北部地区的紧张局势，威胁要重新启动内战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ethiopia-leader-asks-tigray-to-propose-new-head-to-ease-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 11:27:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威的税率计划被通货膨胀挫败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/norway-s-rate-cut-plans-get-foiled-by-inflation-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威的中央银行可能会坚持本周五年来首次削减借贷成本，并受到复兴通货膨胀的挫败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/norway-s-rate-cut-plans-get-foiled-by-inflation-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
