    <item>
      <title>欧洲看到普京强迫特朗普在乌克兰做出艰难的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/europe-sees-putin-forcing-trump-into-a-tough-choice-on-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲官员说，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）很快就会在努力结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争中面临艰难的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/europe-sees-putin-forcing-trump-into-a-tough-choice-on-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 10:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国顶级法院清除了750亿欧元的团结附加费税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/german-top-court-rejects-solidarity-surcharge-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国政府赢得了一项至关重要的法院裁决，该案件可能从公共库存中剥夺了多达750亿欧元（81亿美元）的税收收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/german-top-court-rejects-solidarity-surcharge-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 09:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自入侵以来，奥班顶级外交官第13次前往俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/europeans-are-wary-of-orban-loyalist-s-frequent-trips-to-moscow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）入侵乌克兰以来，匈牙利外交部长彼得·塞吉亚托（Peter Szijjarto）经常访问俄罗斯，以至于欧洲外交官引起了人们的怀疑。他今天回到莫斯科。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/europeans-are-wary-of-orban-loyalist-s-frequent-trips-to-moscow</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 09:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安（Erdogan</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/erdogan-gets-trump-praise-amid-crackdown-that-s-rattled-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）赞扬土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan），向政府承认，在对反对派的镇压下，在国内面临一周的抗议活动和外国资本的逃亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/erdogan-gets-trump-praise-amid-crackdown-that-s-rattled-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 06:20:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CK和Hutchison说，在中国愤怒的情况下继续进行港口交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ck-hutchison-is-said-to-proceed-with-port-deal-despite-china-ire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[熟悉此事的人们说，CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd.计划将两个巴拿马港口出售给Blackrock Inc.领导的集团正按计划前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/ck-hutchison-is-said-to-proceed-with-port-deal-despite-china-ire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 02:06:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在数周而不是几个月内权衡铜进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，美国对铜进口的关税可能会在几周内，比判决的截止日期提前几个月。在纽约交易的铜升至纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/trump-may-implement-copper-import-tariffs-within-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 01:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
